query:
SELECT
                number,
                pubdata_input,
                sealed_at
            FROM
                l1_batches
            LEFT JOIN
                data_availability
                ON data_availability.l1_batch_number = l1_batches.number
            WHERE
                eth_commit_tx_id IS NULL
                AND number != 0
                AND data_availability.blob_id IS NULL
            ORDER BY
                number
            LIMIT
                $1
